text.tspan: Profiling shares of the traditional top six clubs' transfer activity, charting the course of the '10/11 - '18/19
seasons (N.B. '18/19 season includes summer window activity only). Circles represent a season's transfer
business, demonstrating transfer sales (horizontal axis) vs transfer spend (vertical axis).
